Path: godot/classes/class_openxrframesynthesisextension.rst  
Summary: Properties and their default values for the OpenXRFrameSynthesisExtension class.  

- enabled (bool): Controls whether the frame synthesis extension is active. Default: false.  
- relax_frame_interval (bool): Allows more flexible timing between frames. Default: false.
